
/*****************************************************************************/

  This README is an attempt to keep the house clean under the 'js' directory.

  Last update: 2009/03/25

/*****************************************************************************/

Directory contents
-------------------
+ js/

  - autoexpand.js :
    Autoexpanding textarea code and other functions used throughout
    the translate page (writespecial, copyoriginaltranslation).

    Autoexpanding functions may not be needed and other functions can
    be rewritten using jQuery.

  - correctpng.js :
    Fixes for IE 5.5 & 6 to correctly handle PNG transparencies.

    http://homepage.ntlworld.com/bobosola

  - search.js :
    Code to handle the advanced search dropdown. May be merged with other code
    in the translate page.

  - sorttable.js :
    Sorts tables according to its values. Used in the homepage as well as on the
    languages and projects listings.

  - suggestions.js :
    Handles suggestions doing XMLHttpRequest calls using jQuery. Used in the
    translate page and must be nuked by a new implementation. May be merged with
    other code in the translate page.

  - unfuzzy.js :
    Automatically unchecks the fuzzy mark when an edit is detected in a fuzzy
    entry. Used in the translate page. May be merged with other code in the
    translate page.

    A new implementation would be better:
    http://bugs.locamotion.org/show_bug.cgi?id=473

  + jquery/

    - jquery.color.js :
      jQuery Color Animations plugin, used in the translate page when accepting
      and rejecting suggestions. Not really needed, but eye-candy.

      http://plugins.jquery.com/project/color

    - jquery.growfield2.ycomp.js :
      jQuery Growfield2 plugin, used in the translate page textareas.

      http://code.google.com/p/jquery-dynamic/

    - jquery.min.js :
      The jQuery library, version 1.2.6, minified. Bumping to 1.3.1 should be a
      good move.

